<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT81">
<l>katavu maṉameṉṟuṅ kāṇalā meṉṟuṅ</l>
<l>kutaiyum viṉaiyāvi tīrntēṉ vitaiyāka</l>
<l>naṟṟamiḻai vittiye ṉuḷḷattai nīviḷaittāy</l>
<l>kaṟṟamoḻi yākik kalantu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Sowing the good Tamil as a seed, becoming the language [that I] learned,</l>
<l>becoming absorbed [in me], You caused my heart to sprout.</l>
<l>I have become freed from the mind whose work is to bewilder,</l>
<l>which [sometimes] thinks, ‘The heart is a door [preventing the vision of Him]’,</l>
<l rend="indent">And [at other times] thinks, ‘it is possible to see [Him]’.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
